data.description:
Welcome to your two family house dream investment opportunity in Seaside Heights, where coastal charm meets lucrative returns! This property is conveniently rented already for the entire season! Nestled in a prime location with breathtaking bay views and walking distance to the beach, this multi-family property is a true gem that promises both tranquility and a steady stream of income. Meticulously renovated with over $100,000 in upgrades within the past year, this beach property is the epitome of modern comfort and style.

This property has undergone a comprehensive transformation, featuring a brand-new roof with a 20-year warranty, a tankless water heater for efficiency, and a state-of-the-art HVAC system to keep residents comfortable year-round. The convenience continues with a new washer and dryer, as well as upgraded windows and doors, ensuring both energy efficiency and modern aesthetic appeal.
The first-floor unit boasts three spacious bedrooms and a luxurious full bathroom, providing an ideal living space for both residents and potential tenants. Ascend to the second unit, where you'll find another three bedrooms and two beautifully appointed bathrooms, ensuring ample accommodation for occupants and guests alike.
Location is paramount, and this property excels in that regard. Positioned across from the bay, residents will enjoy stunning water views and serene surroundings. The proximity to the boardwalk and beach means endless days of seaside enjoyment, creating an unparalleled lifestyle for residents. Conveniently located near shopping centers and all major highways, this property offers the perfect blend of convenience and leisure.

Investors, rejoice! With its strategic location, recent renovations, and the potential for dual rental income, this multi-family beach property is not just a home; it's a lucrative opportunity waiting to be seized. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of Seaside Heights paradise while reaping the rewards of a sound real estate investment. Act now, and let this seaside haven become your next success story.
